Package hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.scripting.exec

Class ValueWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.scripting.exec.ValueWrapper

  • public class ValueWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a wrapper of any objects, null included.
    Provides numeric operations that can be executed only if the value stored and the operand are null, instances of Integer, Double or String where strings must be able to be parsed into a numeric value.
    If one of the operands is of type Double than the result value is stored as Double and if they are both of type Integer than the result is stored as Integer.
    Author:
    Dorian Ivankovic
